<div id="pf4490" class="pf w47 h2fe" data-page-no="4490"><div class="pc pc4490 w47 h2fe"><div class="t m146f x15 h5 y2f4b ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 13 September 23-29 </div><div class="t mbae x7 h309 y23b3 ff4 fs62 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">f r e </div><div class="t m671 x26 h5 y555 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;I come as a thief. Blessed is he that </div><div class="t mb1d x27 h5 y5cd ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">watcheth&quot; (Rev. 16:15). </div><div class="t m6ad x26 h35 y5b2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This scripture has a double </div><div class="t m552 x27 h35 y14c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">application. First, the end of the </div><div class="t maa4 x27 h35 y558 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">investigative judgment and of the </div><div class="t mb14 x27 h35 y435 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">close of probation will come sooner </div><div class="t m826 x27 h35 yf8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">than many expect, and many people </div><div class="t m785 x27 h35 y75b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">will be caught unprepared. Second, </div><div class="t me5f x27 h35 y29c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for every human being the end of </div><div class="t mb0e x27 h35 y334 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">probation and grace comes at the day </div><div class="t m814 x27 h35 y286 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of his death, and none is sure of his life </div><div class="t m167d x27 h35 ya26 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for one hour. </div><div class="t m120 x26 h35 y8b6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In our past lesson we saw that the </div><div class="t m272 x27 h35 y17b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">basis of the preparation we need for </div><div class="t m5d2 x27 h35 y1229 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the coming crisis is our devotional life: </div><div class="t m2ab x27 h35 ya5f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">enough time dedicated every day, </div><div class="t m23d x27 h35 y38b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">preferably in the early hours of the </div><div class="t m187 x27 h35 y5b7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">morning, to be alone with God and </div><div class="t m337 x27 h35 ye ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">with Christ in the study of the Word </div><div class="t m6ad x27 h35 ya61 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and in secret prayer. </div><div class="t m81d x26 h35 y26a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">As a necessary corollary, this </div><div class="t m8ad x27 h35 y55e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">devotional life that puts us in a very </div><div class="t m41a x27 h35 y588 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">close connection with Christ will </div><div class="t m113 x27 h35 y91c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">produce in our lives the following </div><div class="t m6b8 x27 h35 y96 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">elements: complete surrender, </div><div class="t maa4 x27 h35 y1c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cleansing from sin, victory over </div><div class="t m9d6 x27 h35 y5c5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">weaknesses and defects of character, </div><div class="t m194 x27 h35 y356 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">obedience, and a diligent application </div><div class="t mb8 x27 h35 y21 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to witnessing. And these are the </div><div class="t mb47 x11 h35 y28 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">subjects we shall review in order to </div><div class="t m6c7 x27 h35 y74 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">complete the study of how to be </div><div class="t m999 x11 h35 yba4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">prepared for the coming crisis. </div><div class="t m1d5 x18 h35 y77 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">To try to obtain the necessary </div><div class="t m234 x11 h35 y1474 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">preparation when we are already in </div><div class="t mdd8 x11 h35 y36f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the midst of the crisis will be too late. </div><div class="t m12b x27 h35 y5f3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The five foolish girls who went to buy </div><div class="t mdaf x11 h35 y3c5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">oil during the brief time of waiting </div><div class="t m188 x11 h35 y508 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">discovered that unfortunately they </div><div class="t m425 x11 h35 y628 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">arrived too late at the gates of the </div><div class="t m3c6 x11 h35 y445 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">house in which the wedding had </div><div class="t m5d4 x11 h35 y41 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">already begun, and they were not </div><div class="t ma33 x11 h35 ye1e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">admitted. </div><div class="t m530 x8 h35 y1ed ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Now is the time to be prepared. </div><div class="t m94 x70 h35 y5cd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Now is the day of salvation. </div><div class="t ma23 x8 h35 y5de ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Now is the time to watch and to put </div><div class="t m18f x56 h35 y5b2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">on the garments of the righteousness </div><div class="t m546 x70 h35 y14c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of Christ. Now is the time to put forth </div><div class="t m233 x70 h35 yac ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">every effort to attain, by the grace of </div><div class="t m5f3 x56 h35 y435 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God, the spiritual stature necessary </div><div class="t m826 x70 h35 yd7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for heaven. </div><div class="t m70b x8 h35 y1072 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The time for a happy reunion in the </div><div class="t m9ce x56 h35 y4c2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">kingdom of God will soon come. But </div><div class="t m229 x56 h35 y334 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">while we are still on the road to </div><div class="t mf5e x56 h35 y48a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">heaven, we need to work out our </div><div class="t ma50 x56 h35 ya26 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;salvation with fear and trembling&quot; </div><div class="t m752 x56 h35 y8b6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Phil. 2:12). It depends completely on </div><div class="t m3a3 x56 h35 y17b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">our choice whether in that day we shall </div><div class="t m3c5 x56 h35 y1229 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">find ourselves ready for translation, or </div><div class="t m337 x56 h35 ya5f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">whether God will not let us into His </div><div class="t m8cc x56 h35 yab5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">eternal kingdom. </div><div class="t m5fd x56 h5 y5e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m23f x56 h5 ye1c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m328 x22 h5 ye1c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Self-denial </div><div class="t m8a0 x22 h5 y26a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Matt. 16:24) </div><div class="t m558 x56 h5 y9d1 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m87a x22 h5 y55e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Cleansing From Sin </div><div class="t m54c x9f h5 y41f ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Matt. 9:2) </div><div class="t mb7 x56 h5 y91c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m8df x22 h5 y20 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Total Victory </div><div class="t me06 x9f h5 ye7 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Jude 24) </div><div class="t m1ce x56 h5 y1e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m382 x9f h5 y1e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Obedience </div><div class="t mf3f x9f h5 y291 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Matt. 3:7, 8) </div><div class="t m8a8 x56 h5 y1b53 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m39f x22 h5 y355 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A Work of Witnessing </div><div class="t mf49 x9f h5 yfdd ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Matt. 21:28) </div><div class="t m2ef x7 h5 y253 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t me94 x9f h5 y253 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A Wonderful Reunion </div><div class="t m9d4 x9f h5 y1e0 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 7:9, 10) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
